{
  "stem": "13584.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my son is dating somebody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My daughter is dating, not dating, I don't know right now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we're happy with it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my daughter works for IBM.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My wife is presently the owner of the International Daily Lilburn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My son is the manager there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And before that, my wife-- my wife, by the way, was also a teacher of Russian in Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She was the teacher of the year in Legnica.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She was a very good teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, but when we came to United States, she had to take care of the kids.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So she was in the beginnings, in the beginnings a few years, she was a resident manager of apartments.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So she could take care of manage-- apartments, earn some money, earn the apartment, and take care of the children, look over the children, which was great, which was absolutely great.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then, she changed her profession.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She went back to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She get her master's.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she became a medical technologist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She was-- she-- she became-- she was working for, I think, 14 years or 15 years for Georgia Baptist Hospital.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then, she worked for Northlake Medical Center.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She was the supervisor of the night shift.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But for reasons-- I don't know if it's relevant-- for reasons, she could not stand how the insurance companies are dictating to doctors how long a-- a patient should stay in a hospital.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that got-- she got frustrated with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she decided to take care of-- the next best thing she can do is to cook.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she does marvelous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's a different story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Back in Rome, when we-- all the refugees came from Poland when they received-- by the way, we did not receive a-- a passport to leave Poland.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
